Subprog AS_DUECOD(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TITADI(GBOUT1,"10561") From TRTDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(12276,GBOUTP) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUTA) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_DUECOD(VALEUR) From SUBORG
If mkstat=2
 [M]DUECOD(INDIC) = VALEUR
 Affzo DUECOD(INDIC) : mkstat = 2
Endif
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_DUECOD(zc) From W1ORG3
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_DUECOD(zc) From W1ORG3
Onkey 144 Titled GBOUTP Call P_DUECOD(zc) From W1ORG3
Onkey 146 Titled GBOUTA Call SA_DUECOD(zc) From W1ORG3
